## ğŸ§  WHAT DOES â€œMASS ACTIVITYâ€ MEAN

Mass activity means
â¡ï¸ Abnormally high number of file actions
â¡ï¸ Within a short time window
â¡ï¸ By a single user, host, or IP

### Types

â€¢ Mass delete
â€¢ Mass upload
â€¢ Mass download

Normal users do few actions slowly
