## ğŸ§  HOW SOC DECIDES LEGIT vs MALICIOUS (KEY LOGIC)

Ask these questions ğŸ‘‡

âœ” Who is the user (human vs service)
âœ” From where (internal vs external IP)
âœ” How fast (minutes vs hours)
âœ” What tool (browser vs script)
âœ” What data (public vs sensitive)

If **2â€“3 answers look wrong**
â¡ï¸ Treat as security incident

